      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784725221887,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Our ranking is\n\n    Problems solved (higher is better)\n    Completion time (earlier is better)\n\nHow do we store both in one score?\n\nOne approcach -> encode both into a single numeric score\n    Score = (problemSolved*largeMultiplier) - completionTime",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Our ranking is\n\n    Problems solved (higher is better)\n    Completion time (earlier is better)\n\nHow do we store both in one score?\n\nOne approcach -> encode both into a single numeric score\n    Score = (problemSolved*largeMultiplier) - completionTime",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
